    <item>
      <title>如何使用非root用户执行docker命令</title>
      <link>https://richard-mf.github.io/aispace.github.io/2018/02/09/docker-without-sudo/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://richard-mf.github.io/aispace.github.io/2018/02/09/docker-without-sudo/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Add the docker group if it doesn&amp;rsquo;t already exist:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo groupadd docker&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add the connected user &amp;ldquo;$USER&amp;rdquo; to the docker group. Change the user name to match your preferred user if you do not want to use your current user:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo gpasswd -a &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;$USER&lt;/span&gt; docker&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Either do a newgrp docker or log out/in to activate the changes to groups.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
